  (b) Let $\p\in \Proj T$ be a homogeneous prime ideal.
  Then $\vphi^{-1}(\p)$ is a homogeneous prime ideal, and $\vphi^{-1}(\p)\supset S_+$ implies 
  \[
    \p\supset \vphi(\vphi^{-1}(\p))\supset \vphi (S_+),
  \]
  i.e. $\p\notin U$.
