  Then
  \begin{align*}
    \vphi^{-1}(\p)\ni g\implies \p\supset \vphi(\vphi^{-1}(\p))\ni \vphi(g) \implies \vphi^{-1}(\p)\supset \vphi^{-1}(\vphi(g))\ni g
  \end{align*}
  gives us that
